Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:13.30,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:26.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:33.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:36.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:40.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:44.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:48.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:50.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:54.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:59.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:02.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:11.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:13.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:15.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.16,0:01:18.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.96,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,150.389)}The Monstrous Worm Man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.96,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,680.389)}of the Bottomless Swamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's pulling hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Help me out!\N- All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.37,0:01:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've learned the location\Nof Shocker's secret base!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:02:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't! We don't know\Nwhat you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can stumble on our\Nsecret base and leave here alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are my killer rings!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That should teach you a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The intruders are disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No one must be allowed\Nto approach this base.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Worm Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We will soon begin the\Ncobalt bomb radiation plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,An explosion caused by\Nconventional Cobalt 60...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobalt 120, which contains ten\Ntimes the destructive power,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,will be arriving in Japan soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You were modified from\Na brandling earthworm,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the only organism\Nknown to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the hydrogen bomb\Nexperiments on Bikini Atoll.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, you are the only one\Nwho can carry out this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You carry a heavy burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I will conduct the handover of the\NCobalt 120 at the 51st Wharf today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You will then take command.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Two more men have gone\Nmissing at Persimmon Swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they fell\Ninto the swamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please!\NThere were two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like it's bottomless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't Persimmon Swamp
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the place they found those fissures\Nin the ground six months ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right, Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They thought it was a sign of\Na big earthquake coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Taki, but could you investigate\Ndeeper into the patterns they saw then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You think the disappearances\Nare connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure,\Nbut investigate as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:33.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please move swiftly and pay\Nattention to the signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the scramble crossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:42.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If you intend to cross, please move\Nswiftly and pay attention to the signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that, Sabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tatsu. How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're creeping me\Nout, Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Total success!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Feast your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, how much do you\Nthink it'll fetch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In my opinion...\Nten million at the very least!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten million!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Keep your voice down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the stupidest\Nman I've ever known!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and drive! Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're\Ndriving, jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take that!\N- Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you! You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're way past morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's gotten lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A chocolate bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too hard to be chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!\NYou got the wrong case!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They went that way, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, don't let that\Ncar out of your sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, you jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Persimmon Swamp is\Nclose to the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so people thought it could be the influence\Nof something happening on the sea floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the time investigators came\Nby, the rumblings had died down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This topography... it's the kind of\Nplace they might set up shop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean... Shocker could be\Nbehind the disappearances?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You let some strange men get\Ntheir hands on the Cobalt 120?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You will pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the man\Nwho took our case!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to fret, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this, a masquerade ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be taking our jewels\Nback, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Give us that case!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we could just trade\Ncases and be on our way,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think you need\Nto learn some manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabu, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you,\Nwearing that worm monster mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a carnival, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's not a mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The swamp we're looking\Nfor is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!\NWhat are you plotting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Hand over the\Ncase that man is carrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Case?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you struggle,\Nthe tighter it becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to breathe,\Nisn't it, Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:17.15,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:44.32,Italics,,0,0,0,,I lost... he beat me completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:47.12,Italics,,0,0,0,,But why did the ring come off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:51.22,Italics,,0,0,0,,How did I get it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I commend you for\Ndefeating the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But how could you have\Nlost the Cobalt 120?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your forgiveness.\NI will retrieve it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And how will you do\Nthat, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use this man as a hostage to\Nlure that hoodlum Saburo to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me, please!\NSpare me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell,\Nthe Kamen Rider survives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And the stolen Cobalt 120\Nis with Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You must retrieve it\Nfrom him at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.86,Italics,,0,0,0,,How did I get the ring off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:56.82,Italics,,0,0,0,,I need to figure out how I removed\Nthis ring as soon as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,or the next time we\Nfight, he'll kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you figure out\Nwhat was in the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's incredibly radioactive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Cobalt 120, whose radioactivity\Ngreatly outstrips that of Cobalt 60.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:15:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker is going to use\Nit to create a new bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clear that we must keep\Nit out of Shocker's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... what's gonna\Nhappen to Boss Nogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll save him. Right, Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a little bit more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to die,\Nbring us the Cobalt 120.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go and steal the cobalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hongo and Taki try to stop\Nyou, make them drink poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look inside your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison... in my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:27.42,Italics,,0,0,0,,My entire nervous system was focused on\Nmy neck, as I tried to get the ring off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:37.64,Italics,,0,0,0,,Of course... in that instant,\NI hit my power switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,I used Rider Power\Nto break the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Saburo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an odd duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Saburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying and tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shocker gave me...\Nthis poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish them this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburo betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Saburo betrayed us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll kill this man and\Ntake back the Cobalt 120 myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, I'm going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!\NDid you come here to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker. Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me! Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, the monster is\Nheading for the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Worm Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:19.93,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:23.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:26.72,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:30.50,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:34.25,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:37.73,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:40.33,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:43.93,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:48.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:52.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:02.72,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:06.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:09.85,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:13.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:17.01,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:20.78,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.54,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:27.01,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:31.41,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:35.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:45.92,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:49.19,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:53.08,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:56.61,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:21:00.37,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:03.96,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:06.64,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:10.29,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:14.76,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:18.37,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:33.77,Italics,,0,0,0,,Now... Rider Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Power! Rider Power! \NRider Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about all the trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.49,0:22:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with those two, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's quite a moving\Nreunion, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they must've known\Neach other a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Male friendship, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they learn their lesson and\Ngive up their life of crime. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.61,0:22:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.82,0:22:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So happy! So happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:23:00.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The heroic actions of the Kamen\NRider, Hongo Takeshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.13,0:23:02.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,prevented Shocker from\Nrealizing their radiation plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:05.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker's attacks\Nwould continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:08.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Keep fighting, our Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:10.81,Cont,,0,60,160,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:13.03,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:16.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:18.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the eerie Owl Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.80,0:23:22.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The explosive energy of the\NX-rays built into his eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:24.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,causes clock towers all\Nover the country to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:28.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The\NMonstrous Owl Man's Killer X-Rays."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.36,0:23:31.11,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy80\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(467.167,720.389)}The Eerie Owl\NMan's Killer X-Rays
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:40.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:43.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:45.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:48.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:50.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:52.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:23:54.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.44,0:23:55.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:58.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:04.05,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:07.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,0:24:11.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.67,0:24:15.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Worm Man\Nof the Bottomless Swamp!
Comment: 0,0:23:28.87,0:23:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eerie Owl\NMan's Killer X-Rays